title: Breathe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Store within yoga studio with a juice bar and ready-made cold foods including raw, macro, vegetarian, and vegan. Main entrees, desserts, fresh juices, smoothies. Many of the entrees with meat can be customized to include seitan or tofu instead. Staff is knowledgeable about vegan options.
